research/history/round_summaries/round_0207.json:25:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u4e25\u683c\u6ee1\u8db3\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u539f\u5219\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r201 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE`\u3002\u4e4b\u6240\u4ee5\u4e0d\u7ee7\u7eed\u7559\u5728 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` \u4e0a\u8865 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.5` \u6216\u518d\u626b\u522b\u7684\u5c40\u90e8\u8f74\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a r201/r205/r206 \u5df2\u7ecf\u5f62\u6210\u8db3\u591f\u6e05\u695a\u7684\u95ed\u73af\uff1a\u66f4\u591a cleanup \u9884\u7b97\u66f4\u5dee\uff0c\u66f4\u5f3a coarse \u9884\u7b97\u867d\u66f4\u597d\u4f46\u4e5f\u53ea\u628a objective \u538b\u5230 0.396941\uff0c\u4ecd\u672a\u8fdb\u5165\u65b0\u7684 regime\u3002\u76f8\u6bd4\u4e4b\u4e0b\uff0c`lowrank_expert_topk K=64 A=2 L=160 TR=16` \u4ecd\u662f\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u503c\u5f97\u8865\u7684\u4e00\u6761 matched lane\uff1a\u5b83\u6709\u66f4\u4f4e exact cost\uff08\u7ea6 0.20x\uff09\uff0c\u5e76\u4e14 family \u7684\u5df2\u6709 current-target \u4fe1\u53f7\u6ca1\u6709\u5728\u8fd9\u4e2a exact recipe \u4e0a\u88ab\u76f4\u63a5\u9a8c\u8bc1\u3002\u76f8\u6bd4\u53e6\u4e00\u6761\u53ef\u9009\u7684\u65b0\u69fd\u4f4d `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`\uff0c\u5b83\u66f4\u8d34\u8fd1\u5f53\u524d 0.18x-0.22x \u4e3b\u6218\u573a\uff1b\u540e\u8005\u672c\u5730 exact cost \u5df2\u5728\u7ea6 0.23x\uff0c\u8fdb\u5165\u8fd9\u8f6e\u524d\u5c31\u5df2\u7ecf\u66f4\u8d35\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u662f `lowrank_expert_topk` \u7684 exceed \u4e5f\u7ef4\u6301\u5728 0.188 \u5de6\u53f3\uff0c\u4ece\u800c\u53ea\u80fd\u505a\u5230\u63a5\u8fd1\u4f46\u96be\u4ee5\u8d8a\u8fc7 incumbent\uff1b\u4f46\u5373\u4f7f\u5982\u6b64\uff0c\u8fd9\u8f6e\u4e5f\u80fd\u66f4\u660e\u786e\u5730\u56de\u7b54\u5f53\u524d low-cost \u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u91cc\u201ctrunk+expert vs coarse+cleanup\u201d\u8c01\u66f4\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728\u540c\u4e00 family \u5185\u90e8\u6d88\u8017\u9884\u7b97\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0207.json:72:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u4e25\u683c\u6ee1\u8db3\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u539f\u5219\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r201 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE`\u3002\u4e4b\u6240\u4ee5\u4e0d\u7ee7\u7eed\u7559\u5728 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` \u4e0a\u8865 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.5` \u6216\u518d\u626b\u522b\u7684\u5c40\u90e8\u8f74\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a r201/r205/r206 \u5df2\u7ecf\u5f62\u6210\u8db3\u591f\u6e05\u695a\u7684\u95ed\u73af\uff1a\u66f4\u591a cleanup \u9884\u7b97\u66f4\u5dee\uff0c\u66f4\u5f3a coarse \u9884\u7b97\u867d\u66f4\u597d\u4f46\u4e5f\u53ea\u628a objective \u538b\u5230 0.396941\uff0c\u4ecd\u672a\u8fdb\u5165\u65b0\u7684 regime\u3002\u76f8\u6bd4\u4e4b\u4e0b\uff0c`lowrank_expert_topk K=64 A=2 L=160 TR=16` \u4ecd\u662f\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u503c\u5f97\u8865\u7684\u4e00\u6761 matched lane\uff1a\u5b83\u6709\u66f4\u4f4e exact cost\uff08\u7ea6 0.20x\uff09\uff0c\u5e76\u4e14 family \u7684\u5df2\u6709 current-target \u4fe1\u53f7\u6ca1\u6709\u5728\u8fd9\u4e2a exact recipe \u4e0a\u88ab\u76f4\u63a5\u9a8c\u8bc1\u3002\u76f8\u6bd4\u53e6\u4e00\u6761\u53ef\u9009\u7684\u65b0\u69fd\u4f4d `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`\uff0c\u5b83\u66f4\u8d34\u8fd1\u5f53\u524d 0.18x-0.22x \u4e3b\u6218\u573a\uff1b\u540e\u8005\u672c\u5730 exact cost \u5df2\u5728\u7ea6 0.23x\uff0c\u8fdb\u5165\u8fd9\u8f6e\u524d\u5c31\u5df2\u7ecf\u66f4\u8d35\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u662f `lowrank_expert_topk` \u7684 exceed \u4e5f\u7ef4\u6301\u5728 0.188 \u5de6\u53f3\uff0c\u4ece\u800c\u53ea\u80fd\u505a\u5230\u63a5\u8fd1\u4f46\u96be\u4ee5\u8d8a\u8fc7 incumbent\uff1b\u4f46\u5373\u4f7f\u5982\u6b64\uff0c\u8fd9\u8f6e\u4e5f\u80fd\u66f4\u660e\u786e\u5730\u56de\u7b54\u5f53\u524d low-cost \u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u91cc\u201ctrunk+expert vs coarse+cleanup\u201d\u8c01\u66f4\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728\u540c\u4e00 family \u5185\u90e8\u6d88\u8017\u9884\u7b97\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0175.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family 保持为 `lowrank_expert_topk`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_r β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}`：其中 `{u_r}` 是静态 low-rank trunk 库，`{b_{e,i}}` 是静态 expert 子库原子；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数与轻量 router，再在少量静态 expert 子库内做局部 top-k，最终仍是静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表/加权和 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”链路，因此兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍是 `不兼容`，只能保留历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。当前 `<0.25x` 主战场里，最近的 architecture-level probes `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`、`factorized_topk` 已在 matched low-cost recipe 下给出明确负信号，而 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` / `factorized_expert_topk` 也已有更早低成本负信号；相对之下，`lowrank_expert_topk` 仍是唯一在当前 low-cost 带内离现有 anchor 最近、且尚未完成 trunk 压缩定界的兼容 family。相对 r170 只把 `TRUNK_RANK` 从 `16` 降到 `8`，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`、`K=96`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变，直接回答“低秩 trunk 是否还能进一步左移到约 0.23x，同时保住足够接近当前 0.23x-0.24x anchors 的质量”。，基于当前成本口径复核，该配置仍位于预期成本带内并满足预算约束。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0175.json:25:    "self_review": "这轮严格遵守 param_only 单变量约束：相对 r170 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`。虽然当前策略偏好 architecture-level probe，但最近两轮已经用 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 与 `factorized_topk` 补过新的低成本结构证据，且结果都偏负；继续切向已知低成本负信号更强的 family，信息增量反而更低。选择 `lowrank_expert_topk@TRUNK_RANK=8`，是因为它仍是当前 `<0.25x` 带内最接近现有 anchors 的非主线兼容 family，而 trunk 压缩是尚未完成的高信息量结构轴。主要风险是 rank=8 过薄导致 FVU 明显回退；但若不做这一步，就无法判断这条 family 是否还能在更左的 0.23x 附近保住竞争力。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0175.json:36:      "最近 low-cost architecture probes 已给出更清晰负信号：r172/r174 的 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 仍明显弱于同带 anchors，r173 的 `factorized_topk` 更显著落后；当前不应再让这些 family 主导 `<0.25x` 预算。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0175.json:63:    "self_review": "这轮严格遵守 param_only 单变量约束：相对 r170 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`。虽然当前策略偏好 architecture-level probe，但最近两轮已经用 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 与 `factorized_topk` 补过新的低成本结构证据，且结果都偏负；继续切向已知低成本负信号更强的 family，信息增量反而更低。选择 `lowrank_expert_topk@TRUNK_RANK=8`，是因为它仍是当前 `<0.25x` 带内最接近现有 anchors 的非主线兼容 family，而 trunk 压缩是尚未完成的高信息量结构轴。主要风险是 rank=8 过薄导致 FVU 明显回退；但若不做这一步，就无法判断这条 family 是否还能在更左的 0.23x 附近保住竞争力。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0130.json:7:  "family_name": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0130.json:20:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{j∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=Bx 是 shared low-rank projection，U={u_i} 是静态 shared library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库；在线链路仍可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + 单 expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 仍属直接兼容。唯一主假设：相对 r129 仅把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 从 2 降到 1，在保持 `K=128`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 不变时，shared 分支已覆盖全局主干，routed 分支可以收缩到单 expert 而不显著伤害 FVU，从而把 selection cost 从约 0.24x 压到约 0.16x、total_cost 从约 0.37x 压到约 0.29x，并直接回答这条“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific local top-k”异构 MoE 线是否能形成新的 <0.3x Pareto 段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0130.json:21:    "summary": "已落盘修复 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的 override 接线，使这条新异构 MoE family 可以继续做合法的单变量 param-only 探针。建议本轮以 r129 为 reference，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`，用一次 matched-cost 低开销实验直接检验“shared low-rank basis + 单 routed expert local top-k”是否能把该 family 推进到新的 <0.3x Pareto 段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0130.json:24:    "family_name": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0130.json:38:      "已实际修复 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的 AutoResearch override allowlist；此前该 family 对 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` / `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` / `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 的 param-only probe 会在训练前被判为 disallowed。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0130.json:39:      "本地校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides(..., fallback_architecture='shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk')` 现在接受 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，同时仍拒绝不属于该 family 的 `TRUNK_RANK`。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0130.json:40:      "exact smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward；成本自检为 selection≈0.16x、deploy≈0.12x、total≈0.29x。"
